	(text "This project is a Raspberry pi Pico based pager. The features include:\n- Radio and WiFi communication\n- Support for 8-bit parallel and SPI sreens\n- 12-key keyboard (0-9, cancel, ok)\n- Buzzer\n- Rechargable battery"
